text:
Miss Universe [WATCH] Miss Universe 2016 predictions: Our top 3 picks Miss International Philippines 2014 Bianca Guidotti and pageant blogger Norman Tinio talk about who they think will win on coronation night Published 10:17 AM, January 28, 2017 Updated 10:17 AM, January 28, 2017 Photo by Ethan Miller/Getty Images/AFP 
MANILA, Philippines – The Miss Universe Coronation Night is just around the corner! 
After competing in the preliminaries on January 26, the judges are set to give us their Top 12 on Monday, January 30, at the Mall of Asia Arena. 
Soon after, Pia Wurtzbach will crown her successor – who will it be? Can the Philippines' bet, Maxine Medina, repeat Pia's success? 
Join us on Saturday, January 28, as pageant blogger Norman Tinio and Miss International Philippines 2014 Bianca Guidotti talk about their favorite contenders for Top 3.
